<doc id="352956" wikidata="Q6959511" url="?curid=352956" title="Naibe Reynoso">
<text>Naibe Reynoso is a television reporter and a member of the George Foster Peabody Awards board of jurors.

Naibe Reynoso is a journalist who has won two local Emmys and has been nominated several times. She has worked in Los Angeles, Phoenix and Denver, Colorado. Most recently she hosted &quot;Hola L.A.&quot; on KCAL/CBS an English-language talk show with a Latina point of view.

